net.sf.uadetector
Enum UserAgentType

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<UserAgentType>
      net.sf.uadetector.UserAgentType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<UserAgentType>
public enum UserAgentType
extends Enum<UserAgentType>

This enum represents the type of an user agent. The assignment to a type is performed within the UAS data.

Author:
André Rouél
